snippet.title: HORROR GAME COLLECTION TRAILER | TRIALITY GAMES
snippet.description:
4D - HORROR got upgraded to PSYCHOPATH, there a now tons of new features you can experience. Also, VEINLESS PROPERTY and MAYBE ANOTHER LIFE got minor bug fixes.

This Trailer was especially made for the indie horror game PSYCHOPATH, because of its huge update.

⮞ Download the Games here ⮜

Itch.io: https://triality-games.itch.io/triali...​
Gamejolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/triality-h...​


⮞ Other Links ⮜

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/trialitygames/​
Twitter: https://twitter.com/trialityg​
Itch.io: https://triality-games.itch.io/​
GameJolt: https://gamejolt.com/@TrialityGames​

This horror game collection was made using unity during the first 3 Games 3 Weeks 3 Dudes game jam.
